Karen Khachanov will take on a big challenge at the Internazionali BNL d'Italia on Tuesday when he faces third seed Carlos Alcaraz, the recent Monte-Carlo champion.

Khachanov will try to overcome Alcaraz's 4-0 lead in the pair's Lexus ATP Head2Head series. All of the Spaniard's victories have come in straight sets.



















































































